::FZ::

FZ looks over at the group of Alliance members that had exited the 
CF, seeing that they were all that had entered, and more. He smiles.

"My team will depart now," he says to Iron Raptor, turning to face 
Dark One.

"Dark One, can you return the Maximal hostage to the Maximals?" he 
says to Dark One, ready to leave. All the disobeying of orders in 
this place was making him sick.
